    "en": "The traffic was terrible.",
    "zh": "交通很糟糕。",
    "ja": "交通がひどかったんだ。"
  },
  {
    "time": "00:01:38",
    "en": "No worries.",
    "zh": "沒關係。",
    "ja": "気にしないで。"
  },
  {
    "time": "00:01:39",
    "en": "I just got here too.",
